Package arcade.agent.helper

  • Interface Summary 
    Interface Description
    Helper
    A Helper object is a steppable that interacts with agents.
  • Class Summary 
    Class Description
    ConvertHelper
    Implementation of Helper for converting a cell to a different population.
    InsertHelper
    Implementation of Helper for inserting cell populations.
    MakeTissueHelper
    Extension of TissueHelper for cell division.
    MoveTissueHelper
    Extension of TissueHelper for cell movement.
    RemoveTissueHelper
    Extension of TissueHelper for cell death.
    TissueHelper
    Implementation of Helper for time-delayed TissueCell behaviors.
    WoundHelper
    Implementation of Helper for removing cell agents.
